column2: SELECT TOP #   e.SystemStudentID as StudentID,   e.GradeLevel_Numeric as EnrollmentGrade,   e.SystemStudentID as SchoolYear4Digit,   e.SystemStudentID as Period,   e.SystemStudentID as AssessmentSubject,   e.SystemStudentID as MetricSource,   e.SystemStudentID as MetricName,   e.SystemStudentID as Score,   e.SystemStudentID as IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment as e JOIN TestScores as t ON e.SystemStudentID = t.SystemStudentID
